Search modes:

    1. Attribute mode (Search attributes of files and directories in a given directory)
    2. File content mode (Search contents of a given file)
    3. Directory contents mode (Search the contents of a files in a given directory)
    4. Input mode (Search input text for given pattern)

Operation modes:
    1. Graphics mode (gfxsearch)
    2. Command mode (search or cmdsearch)